io.reinert.requestor.core

Interface SerializationModule


  • public interface SerializationModule
    Module that holds auto-generated Serializers.

    To declare a serialization module you must inherit this class and annotate it with a supported annotation that enables you to specify which classes should have auto-generated serializers.

    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
